      <h3>New Proposal Modal</h3>
      <p>
        Triggered by <strong>+ New Proposal</strong>. A <code>QDialog</code> with a form
        offering: Type (combo of all proposal_type values), Proposed Value (numeric field),
        Justification (multi-line text). On accept, posts to
        <code>POST /api/v2/governance/proposals</code> with <code>effective_date</code>
        defaulting to <code>today + 14 days</code>. The new row appears immediately in the
